Table oms.Shop2FinanceControllerDO

Finance controllers (debtor management systems) that should be used by a shop.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id bigint PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
FinanceControllerDO financeControllerRef integer NOT_NULL The finance controller that should be used. 
ShopDO shopRef bigint NOT_NULL The shop the finance controller should be used for. 
financeControllerShopName varchar(50) NOT_NULL The name of the shop as used by the finance controller instead of defaults. Example "inSPIRED" 
description varchar(250) Further description to the relation between the finance controller and the shop.
